case.name: Question for blue-hairs
case.description: If Miku is playing with anybody with blue hair, she'll ask how their hair got it's color.

case.name: Miku Day
case.description: On March 9th, Hatsune Miku will casually drop the fact that it's "Miku Day", and explains why it's celebrated.

case.name: After-Game Performance
case.description: If any other idols are playing with Miku, she will ask them about doing a performance after the game.

case.name: MoonInTrouble
case.description: When Playing with Bobobo, after his first strip stage, Miku will reference the fact that Moon also tried to do that, but that got her into trouble, so Miku asks why this guy is any different.

case.name: Harry Potter and Mincraft
case.description: Miku explains that some people say that she made Minecraft and wrote Harry Potter, but doesn't have a clue as to why that is.

case.name: Fellow Vocaloids
case.description: Miku talks about some of her Vocaloid friends. The tags denote which one of her friends she's referencinb.

case.name: My Fellow Idols
case.description: If Miku is playing with any other character with the "idol" tag, she'll ask how their recent performances have been?

case.name: After the Performace
case.description: After Finishing, Miku will ask any characters with the "idol" tag about what they like doing after a performance.

case.name: Love Songs
case.description: During the month of Feburary, Miku will ask the other players about their favorite love song.

case.name: My Fellow Musicians
case.description: If Miku is playing with any other musicians (with the exception of Japanese Idols), Miku will ask them about the kinds of music they like performing the most.

case.name: I'm a Vocaloid
case.description: Miku brings up the fact that she's a Vocaloid to the other players.

case.name: A bit of entertainment
case.description: Miku sings a selection her songs for the other players. Use the tags to see which songs she's singing.

case.name: Virtual Endorsement
case.description: If Miku gets a bad hand, she'll talk about various endorsements she's had to do over the years, and how she doesn't really care for them.

case.name: Spooky Songs
case.description: During the Month of October, Miku will sing some of her spookier songs to help celebrate the season.

case.name: Whi... I mean, singing, while you cum.
case.description: Miku makes a spur of the moment decision to make her masturbation more fun: she's going to sing while she does so. (Note, this response is only for the "MasturbationSong" tag.)

case.name: Why you gotta be so short?
case.description: If Miku gets a bad hand, she'll think about how short she is compared to some of the other players in the game.

case.name: Miku's Birthday
case.description: On August 31st, Miku enthusiastically mentions that it's her birthday today.

case.name: Where do the clothes go?
case.description: Miku asks the other players where their clothes go after stripping them.

case.name: Closing Act
case.description: After Finishing, Miku will sing some of her more relaxing songs to help calm herself down.

case.name: The Coolest Thing
case.description: If Miku is playing with an adventurer, she will ask them what the coolest thing they've ever seen was.
